 * 1 - Camera POV Down
 * 7 - Shift Gears 100%

Manipulator Stick Buttons
 * 1 - Open Gripper
 * 2 - Close Gripper
 * 3 - Lift Retractor
 * 4 - Lower Retractor
 * 5 - Kill Lift
 * 6 - NA
 * 7 - Floor Position
